<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your {{appName}} Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .security-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #444;
        }
        .message {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #666;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.4);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.5);
        }
        .security-info {
            background: #f8d7da;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #721c24;
        }
        .expiry-warning {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .no-request {
            background: #d1ecf1;
            border-left: 4px solid #bee5eb;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #0c5460;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { margin: 10px; }
            .header, .content, .footer { padding: 20px; }
            .header h1 { font-size: 24px; }
            .greeting { font-size: 16px; }
            .button { padding: 12px 24px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="security-icon">üîê</div>
            <h1>Password Reset</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hi {{recipientName}},
            </div>

            <div class="message">
                We received a request to reset your {{appName}} account password.
                If you requested this, click the button below to create a new password.
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button">
                    Reset My Password
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="expiry-warning">
                ‚è∞ <strong>Security Notice:</strong> This reset link expires in {{expiryHours}} hour(s) for your account security.
            </div>

            {{#if ipAddress}}
            <div class="security-info">
                <strong>Security Details:</strong><br>
                Request made from IP: <code>{{ipAddress}}</code><br>
                {{#if userAgent}}
                Browser: <code>{{userAgent}}</code><br>
                {{/if}}
                Time: Just now
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="no-request">
                <strong>Didn't request a password reset?</strong><br>
                If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.
                However, if you're concerned about your account security, please contact us immediately.
            </div>

            <div class="message">
                After clicking the reset link, you'll be able to:
                <ul style="color: #666; margin: 15px 0;">
                    <li>Create a new secure password</li>
                    <li>Regain full access to your account</li>
                    <li>Continue planning trips with your groups</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                For security reasons, this link can only be used once and expires in {{expiryHours}} hour(s).
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #dc3545;">{{supportEmail}}</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #999;">
                ¬© {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>